<L>No short swerd for to steke / with poynt bityng</L>
<L>Ne noman ne drawe / ne bere it by his syde</L>
<L N="2548">Ne noman shal / vn-to his felawe ryde</L>
<L>But oo cours / with a sharp I-grounde spere</L>
