<L>Of beldynge / vp-on chirches / may &yogh;e fynde</L>
<L N="1980">If it be good / in Thomas lyf of Ynde<MILESTONE N="89a" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>&YOGH;e lyn here ful of anger / and of Ire</L>
<L>With which the deuele / setteth &yogh;oure hert a-fyre</L>
<L>And chiden heere / the sely Innocent</L>
<L N="1984">&YOGH;oure wyf / that is so meke and pacient</L>
<L>And therfore Thomas / trowe me if &thorn;ou lest</L>
