<L N="2004">vengeaunce is thanne / al that they desire</L>
<L>Ire is a synne on<NOTE PLACE="marg">[on, of, <I>overline, later.</I>]</NOTE> / of the greete of<NOTE PLACE="marg">[on, of, <I>overline, later.</I>]</NOTE> seuene</L>
