<L>vn-to &yogh;oure Holy Couent / whil I lyue</L>
<L>And in thyn hand / &thorn;ou shalt it han a-noone</L>
<L N="2132">On this condicione / and other noone
<PB REF="00000252.tif" N="230"></L>
<L>That &thorn;ou departe it / so / my dere brother</L>
