<L>Is there ought elles / telle me feithfully</L>
<L N="2204">Madame quod he / how thynketh &yogh;ow ther-by
<PB REF="00000254.tif" N="232"></L>
<L>how &thorn;at me thynketh quod she / so god me spede</L>
<L>I seye a cherl / hath doon a cherles dede</L>
