<L N="2256">But loke that it haue / his spokes alle</L>
<L>Twelue spokes hath a cart whel / comounly</L>
<L>And brynge me &thorn;anne twelue freres / wete &yogh;e why<MILESTONE N="92a" UNIT="folio"></L>
